pageProduct.name: Thompson's B Complex 100 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Thompson's B Complex provides valuable support during times of stress.

Thompson's B Complex provides a high potency formulation of B vitamins essential for the maintenance of a healthy nervous system and is commonly used to provide valuable support during times of stress.

Size: 100tabs

KEY FEATURES

• Helps support healthy functioning of the nervous system
• Aids to support the body during times of stress and tension by restoring levels of vitamins B5 & B6
• Assists to provide extra nutritional support to the diet
• Supports energy production
• Vegetarian/Vegan

Warnings

If symptoms persist consult your healthcare professional. Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Each tablet contains:
Thiamine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B1) 5mg
Riboflavin (Vitamin B2) 5mg
Nicotinamide (Vitamin B3) 25mg
Calcium Pantothenate 7.5mg
equiv. Pantothenic Acid (Vitamin B5) 6.9mg
Pyridoxine Hydrochloride 5mg
equiv. Pyridoxine (Vitamin B6) 4.1mg
Cyanocobalamin (Vitamin B12) 5mcg
Folic Acid 90mcg
Biotin 20mcg
Choline Bitartrate 25mg
Inositol 25mg

Directions

Store below 30°C in a dry place. Do not use if bottle and/or cap seal is missing or broken. Keep out of reach of children.

Storage Temperature: Below 30°C

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
